<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>athleti.co | The Transfer Portal for College Football Players</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,700&family=Barlow:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --navy: #0D1B3E;
    --navy-mid: #162347;
    --red: #D81F26;
    --red-dark: #B01820;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --off-white: #F4F5F7;
    --gray: #8A9BB5;
    --gray-light: #E8ECF3;
    --gold: #F5A623;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--white);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ─── NAV ─── */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 1000;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 0 48px;
    height: 72px;
    background: rgba(13,27,62,0.96);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .nav-logo img { height: 40px; }

  .nav-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 4px;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-tabs a {
    display: block;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-tabs a:hover,
  .nav-tabs a.active {
    color: var(--white);
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }

  .nav-tabs a.active {
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--red);
    border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0;
  }

  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--red);
    color: var(--white) !important;
    padding: 9px 22px !important;
    border-radius: 4px !important;
    transition: background 0.2s !important;
  }

  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--red-dark) !important; }

  /* ─── PAGES ─── */
  .page { display: none; padding-top: 72px; min-height: 100vh; }
  .page.active { display: block; }

  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: calc(100vh - 72px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--navy);
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 80% 50%, rgba(216,31,38,0.15) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 60% at 10% 80%, rgba(22,35,71,0.8) 0%, transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #0D1B3E 0%, #162347 50%, #0A1530 100%);
  }

  /* football field lines */
  .hero-bg::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 59px, rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 59px, rgba(255,255,255,0.025) 60px);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 48px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(216,31,38,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(216,31,38,0.4);
    border-radius: 100px;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #FF6B6B;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    width: 6px; height: 6px;
    background: #FF6B6B;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(1.4); }
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(52px, 6vw, 80px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .hero h1 .accent { color: var(--red); }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    max-width: 460px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--red);
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .btn-primary::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(216,31,38,0.4); }
  .btn-primary:hover::after { opacity: 1; }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover { border-color: white; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }

  /* hero stats */
  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 48px;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .hero-stat-num {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 38px;
    color: var(--white);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .hero-stat-num span { color: var(--red); }

  .hero-stat-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* hero right: card mockup */
  .hero-visual {
    position: relative;
    height: 500px;
  }

  .player-card {
    position: absolute;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 16px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    padding: 24px;
    animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px); }
  }

  .card-main {
    width: 280px;
    top: 40px;
    right: 0;
  }

  .card-secondary {
    width: 220px;
    bottom: 60px;
    left: 0;
    animation-delay: 1.5s;
    animation-duration: 3.5s;
  }

  .card-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--red);
    color: white;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .card-player-name {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 22px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .card-position {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gray);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .card-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
  }

  .card-stat-val {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 20px;
  }

  .card-stat-lbl {
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .match-badge {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .match-pct {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: #4ADE80;
  }

  .match-lbl {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .match-school {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ─── SECTION UTILS ─── */
  .section {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 100px 48px;
  }

  .section-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--red);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4vw, 56px);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .section-sub {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  /* ─── HOW IT WORKS ─── */
  .how-bg {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
  }

  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    margin-top: 60px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .step {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 36px 28px;
    position: relative;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }

  .step:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }

  .step-num {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 64px;
    color: rgba(216,31,38,0.15);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .step-icon {
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 20px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .step-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ─── FEATURES ─── */
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .feature-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--red);
    transform: scaleX(0);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
    transform-origin: left;
  }

  .feature-card:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .feature-card:hover::before { transform: scaleX(1); }

  .feature-icon {
    width: 48px; height: 48px;
    background: rgba(216,31,38,0.15);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .feature-title {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 18px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .feature-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(245,166,35,0.15);
    color: var(--gold);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,166,35,0.3);
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .feature-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ─── PRICING ─── */
  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px 32px;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .pricing-card.featured {
    background: rgba(216,31,38,0.1);
    border-color: var(--red);
    transform: scale(1.04);
  }

  .pricing-featured-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -14px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--red);
    color: white;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 16px;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  .pricing-tier {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gray);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .pricing-price {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 52px;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .pricing-price sup { font-size: 24px; vertical-align: top; margin-top: 12px; display: inline-block; }
  .pricing-period { font-size: 14px; color: var(--gray); margin-bottom: 28px; }

  .pricing-features {
    list-style: none;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .pricing-features li {
    padding: 10px 0;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .pricing-features li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .check { color: #4ADE80; font-size: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .cross { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); font-size: 14px; flex-shrink: 0; }

  .btn-outline {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 14px;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover { border-color: white; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }

  .btn-full {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 14px;
    background: var(--red);
    border: none;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-full:hover { background: var(--red-dark); }

  /* ─── COACH PAGE ─── */
  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .coach-feature-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin-top: 36px;
  }

  .coach-feature-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 20px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .coach-feature-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .cfl-icon {
    width: 44px; height: 44px;
    background: rgba(216,31,38,0.12);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 20px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .cfl-title {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .cfl-desc { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); line-height: 1.5; }

  /* dashboard mockup */
  .dashboard-mock {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .dash-header {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    padding: 14px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .dash-dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }

  .dash-body { padding: 20px; }

  .dash-search {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .dash-player-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 12px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  }

  .dash-avatar {
    width: 36px; height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--red);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .dash-pname {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .dash-ppos { font-size: 11px; color: var(--gray); }

  .dash-fit {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #4ADE80;
  }

  /* ─── ABOUT PAGE ─── */
  .about-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D1B3E 0%, #162347 100%);
    padding: 80px 48px 100px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 100% at 50% 0%, rgba(216,31,38,0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }

  .about-hero-content { position: relative; z-index: 1; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .team-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }

  .team-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .team-avatar {
    width: 72px; height: 72px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--red), #8B0000);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 24px;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
  }

  .team-name {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 18px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .team-role { font-size: 13px; color: var(--gray); }

  /* stats row */
  .stats-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }

  .stat-box {
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 40px 32px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 52px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--white);
  }

  .stat-num .red { color: var(--red); }

  .stat-lbl {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer {
    background: #060E20;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    padding: 60px 48px 40px;
  }

  .footer-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
  }

  .footer-logo { margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .footer-logo img { height: 36px; }

<script>
  function showPage(pageId, linkEl) {
    // Hide all pages
    document.querySelectorAll('.page').forEach(p => p.classList.remove('active'));
    document.getElementById('page-' + pageId).classList.add('active');

    // Update nav active state
    document.querySelectorAll('.nav-tabs a').forEach(a => a.classList.remove('active'));
    if (linkEl) linkEl.classList.add('active');

    // Scroll to top
    window.scrollTo(0, 0);
  }

  function switchSignup(type, btn) {
    document.querySelectorAll('.signup-tab').forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
    btn.classList.add('active');
    document.getElementById('player-form').style.display = type === 'player' ? 'block' : 'none';
    document.getElementById('coach-form').style.display = type === 'coach' ? 'block' : 'none';
  }
</script>
